metadata.name: Neph'elleeh
metadata.description:
Neph'elleeh may seem like a woman with a dark side. Don't be prejudiced. You know that in ancient times the serpent represented wisdom and today its meaning has been defiled. 

She is simply a woman who offers her heart to knowledge and wisdom.. 

And this Neph'elleeh's heart? 

The answer to that is a secret between this lady and me!
